You can go northwest, north or southwest.
This is where you learn what is going to happen. After defeating the monster, you learn that the king is taking the throne and collecting the spoils of the monster you defeated. You don't want this to happen, so you must claim the throne before the king does. You have 500 turns to claim the throne before the king gets his hands on it.
> take boiled item
A boiled item is yours. Remember to use it if you're low on health.
> look at secret alley

You can go northwest or east.
Hello and welcome to the Battle Challenge! This is a challenge where you battle a training dummy to earn money! Simple! But each unsuccessful attack will drop your health! You can only bring the items you take in once you enter. Are you ready for a challenge? Well, you must pay $2000 to enter. Are you ready?
Hello! Fancy taking on the Battle Challenge? It will cost you $2000 to enter, and you can only use the items you have once inside. Are you ready?
> east

OK Then! It's time to defeat your dummy!
