You can go northwest or east.
Hello! Fancy taking on the Battle Challenge? It will cost you $2000 to enter, and you can only use the items you have once inside. Are you ready?
That's the end of your Battle Challenge! Better than a trip to Throne Jail, but the money you earned was well worth it! Fancy another round? It will cost you $2,000.
