You can go southeast.
The king has respawned! The king will take varied attacks each so often and will attack more than once, so you'll need restoration items to see you through the fight. After each attack, you have a 1% chance of defeating the king. If you defeat the king, you escape!
> look at king ex
You defeated the King! This will come as no surprise, as you are one of its true rulers. You mastered the hardest game yet, and now, you succeeded.

THE END.
You attacked the king, but it was a weak blow.
You attacked the king. Welcome to Throne Jail- truly!
